115
00:08:21,470 --> 00:08:23,700
I'm going to meet the designer this afternoon.

116
00:08:23,700 --> 00:08:25,720
Aren't you going off to film next month?

117
00:08:25,720 --> 00:08:26,480
So I thought

118
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,500
