184
00:11:50,340 --> 00:11:51,940
Don't laugh.

185
00:11:51,970 --> 00:11:53,260
I'm being serious.

186
00:11:53,830 --> 00:11:55,690
I even specifically consulted this afternoon,

187
00:11:55,690 --> 00:11:57,890
