190
00:12:02,260 --> 00:12:03,350
I'm learning

191
00:12:03,380 --> 00:12:04,690
as I go with

192
00:12:04,710 --> 00:12:06,070
the books and yoga.

193
00:12:06,690 --> 00:12:08,020
With me supporting you,

194
00:12:08,170 --> 00:12:10,220
I hope to make things a bit easier for you,

195
00:12:10,220 --> 00:12:12,150
both mentally and in terms of time.

196
00:12:14,040 --> 00:12:15,890
So you already knew?

197
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:25,640
This morning,

198
00:12:25,670 --> 00:12:27,070
