for the next few months.

215
00:12:53,920 --> 00:12:55,380
Even if he does, I won't go.

216
00:12:55,740 --> 00:12:56,840
When you join the crew next month,

217
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:57,970
I'll go with you.

218
00:12:59,910 --> 00:13:01,950
I thought this was supposed to be a surprise.

219
00:13:01,950 --> 00:13:03,260
It is a surprise!

220
00:13:03,290 --> 00:13:05,260
Come on, eat while it's hot.

221
00:13:05,280 --> 00:13:06,020
Otherwise, it'll get cold.

222
00:13:06,020 --> 00:13:07,800
This one is yours.

223
00:13:08,230 --> 00:13:09,230
And this one...

224
00:13:09,250 --> 00:13:10,560
is for our baby.

225
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:23,680
[Domestic Arrivals]

226
00:13:23,840 --> 00:13:25,770
Didn't you say you'd be here early?

227
00:13:25,770 --> 00:13:27,580
Why show up so late?

228
00:13:27,610 --> 00:13:29,600
Couldn't you have booked an earlier flight?

229
00:13:29,600 --> 00:13:31,240
What's wrong with you? Stop!

230
00:13:31,530 --> 00:13:32,960
Tell me, what's going on with you?

231
00:13:32,960 --> 00:13:34,550
The floor was just mopped.

232
00:13:34,550 --> 00:13:36,210
Couldn't you lift your suitcase?

233
00:13:36,210 --> 00:13:37,360
Alright, alright, I got it.

234
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:38,360
What do you mean "I got it"?

235
00:13:38,360 --> 00:13:39,720
Can you just watch your tone?

236
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:40,230
How could you...

237
00:13:40,230 --> 00:13:41,050
What's wrong with you?

238
00:13:41,050 --> 00:13:41,920
What are you doing?

239
00:13:41,920 --> 00:13:42,770
Why are you pulling me?

240
00:13:42,770 --> 00:13:43,560
She's my own daughter,

241
00:13:43,560 --> 00:13:44,960
am I not allowed to scold her?

242
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:45,960
Just look at her,

243
00:13:45,980 --> 00:13:47,930
she's carrying such a tiny suitcase.

244
00:13:47,930 --> 00:13:49,550
Even the small suitcase bothers you?

245
00:13:49,550 --> 00:13:51,850
She just got back, just leave her alone.

246
00:13:51,930 --> 00:13:52,960
Bringing only such a small suitcase

247
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:54,620
means she only packed a few clothes,

248
00:13:54,620 --> 00:13:55,620
