260
00:14:15,930 --> 00:14:17,150
This is exactly why

261
00:14:17,150 --> 00:14:18,770
I don’t want to come home.

262
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:20,360
Whether you come back or not is up to you.

263
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:21,620
I honestly don't care.

264
00:14:24,500 --> 00:14:25,390
You...

265
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:28,150
Why are you here alone? Xing didn't come along?

266
00:14:28,150 --> 00:14:29,560
Is Xing busy with something,

267
00:14:29,560 --> 00:14:30,560
so he couldn't come back?

268
00:14:30,560 --> 00:14:32,030
What has he been busy with lately?

269
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:32,920
You're so funny.

270
00:14:32,920 --> 00:14:35,240
How can you change your attitude so quickly?

271
00:14:35,240 --> 00:14:37,130
One might think he's your own son,

272
00:14:37,160 --> 00:14:38,610
and I'm some kind of bullied daughter-in-law.

273
00:14:38,610 --> 00:14:40,090
Alright, alright, let's not discuss this.

274
00:14:40,090 --> 00:14:42,290
Tell me, why didn't Xing come with you?

275
00:14:42,320 --> 00:14:44,440
-How is he lately?
-He's busy.

276
00:14:45,510 --> 00:14:48,310
Judging by Fei's tone, don't tell me they broke up.

277
00:14:48,620 --> 00:14:50,170
What are you talking about?

278
00:14:53,370 --> 00:14:54,340
No way.

279
00:14:54,710 --> 00:14:56,120
I got it right.

